word_mean_info__list.difference: 与object基本同义，但语义更广泛，指具体或很快能达到的目的，也可指军事目标。书面用词。
从本义“靶子”引申而来，侧重比较具体而明确的目标，但常指短期目标。
指射击的靶，军事攻击目标。引申指被攻击、批评或潮笑的目标。
强调个人或需求而决定的目标、目的。

指心目中怀着的某种目的，强调结果而非过程。较正式用词。
指经过考虑和选择，需经坚持不懈的努力奋斗才能达到的最终目标。

list.abstract: 塔吉特公司（target）是一家美国零售百货集团。 2024年8月5日，2024年《财富》世界500强排行榜发布，target位列第90名。
Romeo第二张专辑主打歌曲《target》于2015年11月5日发行。

yingyinNormal.en: No, the judg is the target. Schakowsky?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不行，法官就是我们的目标。沙考斯基？

yingyinNormal.en: For many months now, my new target has been you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这几个月来，我的新目标就是你。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Church said the target's name was Victor Minns.
yingyinNormal.zh: 教堂说目标的名字叫维克多·明斯。

yingyinNormal.en: And that makes him a target? Objection. Argumentative. Come on.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是否令他成为攻击目标？反对，提问有争议。又来吗。

yingyinNormal.en: Target, opportunity, all the intel you could ask for, and you got decimated and my target walked away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 目标，机会，还有你需要的所有情报可是你，却打了败仗，让目标逃之夭夭。

yingyinNormal.en: When they get on target, and they will get on target, wait to engage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当她们锁定目标，她们一定会锁定等待发动进攻。

yingyinNormal.en: That's my target when I'm by myself and now my target at the new shop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我单身时也是向这些人下手的，而他们现在是我新店的目标客户。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't worry. You're small and weak. That'll make you less of a target.
yingyinNormal.zh: 放心，你太瘦弱，绝对不会是攻击的目标。

yingyinNormal.en: We got one good target, gentlemen. Do not shoot my Raptors. Please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们只有一个目标，先生们，不要伤了我的迅猛龙，拜托了。

yingyinNormal.en: Our target is Owen Shaw. Former major in the S.A.S., Spec-ops soldier.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的目标是欧文·肖，原英国特种空勤队的少校，特种兵。

yingyinNormal.en: State funeral. Must-attend event for western leaders. Each one a target.
yingyinNormal.zh: 国葬仪式，西方领导人必定出席的事件，每个人都是目标。

yingyinNormal.en: Of course wait. I'm the target, targets wait. Look, whatever is coming, whatever he's lined up, I'll know when it begins.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然要等，我是目标，目标就得等，听着，不管会发生什么，他有什么计划，一旦开始，我自然会知道。

yingyinNormal.en: So, as far as the Americans are concern, you're a rogue assassin, a target of opportunity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以至少在美国方面，你是个凶残的杀手，通缉的目标。

yingyinNormal.en: Skipper, look. Above Private. Dave's next target, Shanghai's famous mermaid penguins.
yingyinNormal.zh: 老大，看，菜鸟上面，戴夫的下一个目标，上海著名的企鹅美人鱼。

yingyinNormal.en: Ma'am. The First Order, they're charging the weapon again now. Our system is the next target.
yingyinNormal.zh: 夫人。第一秩序现在正在重新装载他们的武器，下次目标是我们的星系。

yingyinNormal.en: Roll up, roll up. Hit the target and win a giant Teddy. You can do that easy, Mummy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 快来吧，快来吧。只要射中目标就可以有一个大熊猫哦。妈妈，这个你也可以做得到。

yingyinNormal.en: Great. We found a cooling solution that allowed us to get the size of the prototype down to the target specs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很好。我们研究出一个冷却方案可以让原型机的大小缩小至目标规格。

yingyinNormal.en: Entire divisions within the government are using versions of his product, which makes him a prime target for hackers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 政府部门的整个机构都在用他的产品，所以他是黑客的主要目标。

yingyinNormal.en: Keep it simple, eyes on the ball, shoulders up, see your foot hit it, drive through the ball. Finish at your target!
yingyinNormal.zh: 简单点，看着球，抬起肩膀，看见你的脚踢到球，把球踢飞，完成目标！

yingyinNormal.en: We have information that Downtown Chicago is the next target. And they're planning to detonate a dirty bomb.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们得到消息芝加哥市中心是下一个目标，他们准备在市中心引爆放射性炸弹。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It's not difficult to set <highlight>targets</highlight> for staff.
Setting <highlight>targets</highlight> can and does have unforeseen negative consequences.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 设定目标可以而且确实会产生不可预见的负面后果。

examination_example.sentence: This is not an argument against <highlight>target</highlight>-setting.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这不是反对设定目标的理由。

sense_info_list.en: to try to have an effect on a particular group of people

examination_example.sentence: Digital services include everything from providing a platform for selling goods and services online to <highlight>targeting</highlight> advertising based on user data.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 数字服务包括所有内容，从提供在线销售商品和服务的平台到基于用户数据的定向广告。

examination_example.sentence: They'll get less meaningful, less <highlight>targeted</highlight> ads.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们会得到不那么有意义、不那么有针对性的广告。

examination_example.sentence: The European Union Framework funding programs have long had a category specifically <highlight>targeted</highlight> at social scientists.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 欧盟框架资助项目长期以来有一个专门针对社会科学家的类别。

sense_info_list.en: an object that people practise shooting at, especially a round board with circles on it

word_usage.usage:
aim, goal, purpose, target, object, objective 这些名词均有“目标、目的”之意。
aim从本义“靶子”引申而来，侧重比较具体而明确的目标，但常指短期目标。
goal指经过考虑和选择，需经坚持不懈的努力奋斗才能达到的最终目标。
purpose普通用词，既指以坚决、审慎的行动去达到的目的，又指心中渴望要实际的目标。
target指射击的靶，军事攻击目标。引申指被攻击、批评或潮笑的目标。
object强调个人或需求而决定的目标、目的。
objective与object基本同义，但语义更广泛，指具体或很快能达到的目的，也可指军事目标。书面用词。

examination_example.sentence: The project, organized by Student Union, <highlight>targeted</highlight> mainly junior and senior students and attracted many sophomores, too.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该项目由学生会组织，主要针对初高中学生，也吸引了很多大二学生。

examination_example.sentence: They <highlight>target</highlight> groups of men who are considering a career change, such as fathers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们的目标人群是考虑跳槽的男性，比如父亲。

examination_example.sentence: Scotland will reach the national <highlight>target</highlight> in carbon emissions reduction ahead of schedule.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 苏格兰将提前实现碳减排的国家目标。

examination_example.sentence: Some raised more than twice their goals, but others have fallen short of reaching even modest <highlight>targets</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有人筹到了两倍以上的目标金额，但有的人甚至没有达到适度的目标。

examination_example.sentence: So I think that is really the challenge for people who live in a country where their <highlight>target</highlight> language isn't spoken.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所以我认为，对于生活在一个目标语言没有被使用的国家的人来说，这确实是一个挑战。
